CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, August 2, 1938, pg. 18, reads: "Flash Cameraman Feted on Birthday - Surprise - Surprise, that was friends of Teeny [Teenie] Harris, News camera man had to say when they tossed a honey for him a Saturday ago. A candid shot caught Teeney [Teenie] in whirl, in the lower left photo just to the right of the tall dancer on the extreme left. (Photos by 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Men and women dancing, including Charles "Teenie" Harris in center, and Barbara Jones, Helen Phillips, and William "Woogie" Harris in background, for birthday party of Teenie Harris, in Loendi Club
